Class Asearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • Asearch

  • public class Asearch
extends java.lang.Object
    Allows for searching of a given DirectedGraph with an A* search - by using a comparator in order to give weighting to particular state spaces over one another.
    Please note this A* Search is based on the Vector class
    Author:
    Hayden Charles Smith, z3418003
    Last modified: 19th May 2013
